Update	Update	更新
CheckForUpdates	Check for updates	检查更新
AutoUpdate	Auto-update	自动更新
CurrentVersionHeader	Current version: {0}	当前版本：{0}
BuildVersion	Version {0}	版本 {0}
DevelopmentBuild	Development version	开发版本
UpdateChecking	Checking for updates...	正在检查更新...
UpdateCheckFinished	Update check finished.	更新检查已完成。
UpdateAvailableTitle	Update available	发现新版本
UpdateAvailableMessage	Version {0} is available. Install it now? The app will close and restart.	发现版本 {0}。是否立即安装？应用将关闭并重启。
UpdateNoneTitle	No updates	没有更新
UpdateNoneMessage	You are already using the latest version.	当前已经是最新版本。
UpdateFailedTitle	Update check failed	更新检查失败
UpdateFailedMessage	Failed to check for updates: {0}	检查更新失败：{0}
UpdateLaunchFailedMessage	Failed to launch the updater script.	启动更新脚本失败。
SearchWatermark	Search settings and tools	搜索设置和工具
ClearSearch	Clear search	清除搜索
NoSearchResultsInCurrentTab	No matching results in the current tab.	当前标签页没有匹配结果。
Language	Language	语言
Theme	Theme	主题
DefaultFontName	Microsoft YaHei UI, Segoe UI, sans-serif	Microsoft YaHei UI, Segoe UI, sans-serif
OptimizeSelectedItems	Optimize selected items	优化选中项目
OptimizeSelectedItemsWithExcludedCount	Optimize selected items ({0} excluded)	优化选中项目（已排除 {0} 项）
Initializing	Initializing…	正在初始化...
InitializationFinished	Initialization finished.	初始化完成。
InitializationFailed	Initialization failed.	初始化出错。
OperatingItem	Operating: {0}	正在操作：{0}
OperatingItemFinished	Operation finished: {0}	操作完成：{0}
PreOptimizationPreparations	Pre-optimization preparations…	优化前准备工作...
OptimizingItem	Optimizing: {0}…	正在优化：{0}…
PostOptimizationProcessing	Post-optimization processing…	优化后处理…
OptimizationCompleted	Optimization completed!	优化已完成！
PleaseUninstallDriver	Please {0} and restart to continue.	请 {0} 并重启后重试。
